> Native support isn&#x27;t any more concise, in fact it is more verbose when partial application is involved.<p>I only know too well. Everytime I write stuff like<p><pre><code>    using std::placeholders;
    std::bind(foo, bar, _1, _2, baz, _3, _4);
</code></pre>
I wish I were using an applicative language instead.
